My beautiful Scorpio babies!!!

To my beloved Eboni (aka BIG EB) you are such a wonderful and beautiful sweet and sour patch! I enjoy you more and more as I watch you grow and show more of your personality! I am so blessed and grateful to have a soul like yours be my child! You are so smart so hilarious and can’t believe you chose me!!!! I want nothing but the best and to give you love,stability, confidence, wisdom, and fabulousness as you grow!!! THE BIG 2 and ur outside with it honey!!! I wish you many more birthdays of love, happiness, pumpkin patches and parties! (Y’all we been partying all week!) Happy Birthday big Eb!!! Here’s a little slide to show just how wacky my baby is!!!! Mommy loves you to the galaxies and beyond!!!

Paw Patrol came out for Halloween! 
🐶🐶✨✨Chase is on the case and Rubble on the Double!!! My babies are so dag gon cute!!! So of course they won best costume on the block! 😎😏Especially if I got anything to do with it….And did!!! I did their makeup!!! Hey agencies come get these kids in your next spread!!! They are to cute and fun to pass up😉 ✨✨✨ swipe left 👸🏽they had a time Chile 

#halloween #mommy #momlife #pawpatrol #lifestyle

My baby girl and first born has turned 4!!!! Where has the time gone!!!! AMAYAH mommy loves u to life and beyond!!! I will travel the galaxies, the depths of this planet and even fight the worst of demons just to be with you! You are such an amazing, hilarious and beautiful young girl and I’m sooooo proud of you! You are strong you are kind, you are wise and you teach me about life more and more everyday!!!! I wish I can do more and I will work everyday to make sure you have everything you need and more!!! My first born daughter, the start of it all, mommy loves u more than anything! Happy Birthday little bird!!!! Period Pooh *swipe for her birthday extravaganza and a few pix in between* ✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨

I’ve been enjoying my life in the midst of adversity. Thank God for allowing me to have small moments like these and spend it with the ppl I get to share them with.  I’m getting inspired, healed, taking my time until I’m full and then music will come. #operateinlove Until then enjoy the photo dump ✨✨✨#sundayfunday #sundaybrunch #shutterssantamonica
